text: An amazing building and architecture! It is everything a factory and office in Singapore should be. There is lots of natural light and nice open spaces to allow good air flow through the building. Very sensible and definitely very sustainable!

I was there for a company visit due to work and was given a short tour. The management believes in contributing back to the society and treating the employees like family. This is reflected in the interiors and facilities of the company. A rare gem for local SME in my opinion...
This lady boss is a really nice person with good natured heart. I wish to see this company expanding with unstoppable success.
